OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,FThe family of a much-loved father
OL,7,Fstamped to death by a paranoid
OL,8,Fschizophrenic has told a court they
OL,9,Ffeel "let down" by the authorities.
OL,11,FGary Carlisle, 62, was attacked by
OL,12,FJacob Hill, 32, as he walked his dog
OL,13,Fnear his home in Preston, Lancashire,
OL,14,Fon 12 March 2025.
OL,16,FCCTV footage showed Hill left his
OL,17,Faddress at just before 6am and behaved
OL,18,Ferratically before 10 minutes later he
OL,19,Fapproached Mr Carlisle, a stranger,
OL,20,Fwith his arms outstretched.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,FA "plainly frightened" Mr Carlisle
OL,7,Fbacked off and ran away pursued by
OL,8,FHill, who jumped on his back and
OL,9,Fdragged him to the floor, Preston
OL,10,FCrown Court heard.
OL,12,FHill kicked Mr Carlisle when he tried
OL,13,Fto get off the ground and then
OL,14,Flaunched "a sickening display of
OL,15,Fbrutal violence" as he repeatedly
OL,16,Fstamped on his victim's head.
OL,18,FSeveral shocked commuters witnessed
OL,19,Fthe incident including a female bus
OL,20,Fpassenger who confronted Hill and
OL,21,Fshouted: "What are you doing? Stop."
OL,26,@nD@COUnD@VO]vD@JOUwD@PO]}D@JOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,FHill responded with a forceful
OL,7,Fheadbutt to her face, the court heard,
OL,8,Fbefore police and paramedics arrived
OL,9,Fon the scene.
OL,11,FThe woman said the scene was "like
OL,12,Fsomething out of a horror film" as Mr
OL,13,FCarlisle lay face down in a pool of
OL,14,Fblood.
OL,16,FHill was arrested shortly after police
OL,17,Ftwice discharged a Taser at him and
OL,18,Flater told detectives: "I was out of
OL,19,Fmy mind. He was the wrong guy in the
OL,20,Fwrong place."
OL,26,@sD@^OUtD@_O]zD@XOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,FMr Carlisle died a week later in
OL,7,Fhospital from "catastrophic" brain
OL,8,Finjuries.
OL,10,FIn a victim impact statement, his
OL,11,Fsister Jackie Watters told the court:
OL,12,F"He has been snatched away from me. It
OL,13,Ffeels so unfair.
OL,15,F"I can never forget those tens of
OL,16,Fhours sat in the ICU looking at him,
OL,17,Fstroking him ... a man with a swollen
OL,18,Fhead displaying every line, crease and
OL,19,Fbruise.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@\O]tD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,F"The staff said they were the worst-
OL,7,Fever injuries seen in the ICU."
OL,9,FShe added the family believed they had
OL,10,Fbeen let down by authorities who
OL,11,Fallowed Hill to live in the community
OL,12,Fwith "normal people" like her brother.
OL,14,FMr Carlisle's daughter Simone Hartley
OL,15,Fsaid: "I feel as if our lives have
OL,16,Fbeen toppled upside down but he is OK
OL,17,Fand is being treated in hospital.
OL,19,F"He was known to mental health when he
OL,20,Fdid this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]tD@FOUtD@TO]wD@GOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,F"Things need to be different. I do
OL,7,Ffeel we have been let down. Changes
OL,8,Fneed to be made so it doesn't happen
OL,9,Fto someone else."
OL,11,FMukul Chawla KC, defending, said there
OL,12,Fwas "a wealth of evidence" that the
OL,13,Fdefendant sought to address his
OL,14,Fillness in the weeks and days before
OL,15,Fthe fatal attack.
OL,17,FHe said: "He had sought stronger
OL,18,Fmedication. He realised something was
OL,19,Fwrong. That was not even evident to
OL,20,Fthe community health worker at the
OL,21,Ftime."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]tD@EOUtD@ZO]yD@JOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,FHill had no previous convictions but
OL,7,Fwas arrested for assaults in recent
OL,8,Fyears, including some when he was in
OL,9,Fmental health institutions, but none
OL,10,Fresulted in prosecutions.
OL,12,FThe court was told that psychiatrists
OL,13,Ffor the prosecution and defence agreed
OL,14,FHill was suffering from an enduring,
OL,15,Fsevere psychotic illness. It had
OL,16,Fpresented since his late teens and had
OL,17,Fled to multiple admissions to hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,FHill pleaded guilty at an earlier
OL,7,Fhearing to manslaughter by reason of
OL,8,Fdiminished responsibility and assault
OL,9,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,11,FHe is being treated in a high-security
OL,12,Fpsychiatric hospital and is said to be
OL,13,F"currently stable and compliant" on a
OL,14,Fhigh dose of anti-psychotic
OL,15,Fmedication, but is "prone to relapse".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@`O]wD@TOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,FOn Friday, he was sentenced to a
OL,7,Fhospital order with a restriction that
OL,8,Fhe cannot be released into the
OL,9,Fcommunity without the permission of
OL,10,Fthe Secretary of State or a mental
OL,11,Fhealth tribunal.
OL,13,FJudge Robert Altham, Honorary Recorder
OL,14,Fof Preston, told Hill: "I cannot
OL,15,Fimagine how Mr Carlisle's family have
OL,16,Fbeen affected by what you did to him.
OL,18,F"The suddenness of his death and the
OL,19,Fsheer brutality of your actions are
OL,20,Fbeyond any kind of comprehension.
OL,26,@vD@XOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,F"I fear your illness will not lessen
OL,7,Fthe feelings of shock and anger that
OL,8,FMr Carlisle's family must inevitably
OL,9,Ffeel."
OL,11,FHe said Mr Carlisle was a "much-loved
OL,12,Ffather" who was "central" to the lives
OL,13,Fof his family.
OL,15,FIn a tribute issued through Lancashire
OL,16,FPolice, Mr Carlisle's family said:
OL,17,F"Gary always believed and spoke about
OL,18,F'when it was his time, it was his
OL,19,Ftime'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]sD@[OUtD@GO]tD@QOUtD@YO]yD@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,F"He would never have believed that his
OL,7,Flife would have ended the way it did
OL,8,Fthough.
OL,10,F"All he would have been thinking on
OL,11,Fthat day was how to get his dog back
OL,12,Fhome and get away from what was
OL,13,Fhappening. He didn't deserve what
OL,14,Fhappened to him.
OL,16,F"We cannot thank the community enough
OL,17,Fwith how supportive they have been
OL,18,Fduring this horrific time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777126304
OL,3,CFamily 'feel let down' over death of
OL,4,Cman killed by mentally-ill stranger
OL,6,F"We had hundreds of people arrive for
OL,7,FGary's funeral and have since had
OL,8,Fmemorial events where hundreds have
OL,9,Fattended to show support and an
OL,10,Foutpouring of love for Gary.
OL,12,F"That shows what kind of man he was."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
